> ## Hints from an ECS Teacher:
> Think back to Unit 1 when students explored what a computer is.  This activity is very similar but with discovering what is a robot.  What worked for you when you taught that lesson or what would you change now that you get the opportunity to do something similar?
 
## Things to keep in mind 
Consider what real world connections you can use to help your students relate to robotics.  Think of movies that you've seen robots in, jobs that utilize robots, and how robots are changing society? 

